  "novel_contributions": [
    "We propose Vision Mamba (Vim), which incorporates bidirectional SSM for data-dependent global visual context modeling and position embeddings for location-aware visual understanding.",
    "Without the need of attention, the proposed Vim has the same modeling power as ViT while it only has subquadratic-time computation and linear memory complexity.",
    "We conduct extensive experiments on ImageNet classification and dense prediction downstream tasks.",
